{"id":261858,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/维权网-四川上访维权者在省委门口展示我们要/","date":"2012-11-08T11:01:07Z","modified":"2012-11-08T11:01:07Z","title":"维权网 | 四川上访维权者在省委门口展示“我们要生存”横幅（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员陈华报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日下午</span><span>，四川省西充县何琼等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>人躲过当地官员对他们的跟踪监控，来到成都市省委省政府办公地，再次展示“我们要生存，我们要货款”的横幅，并采用静坐抗议的办法表达自己的诉求。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>大家的维权行动很快被门口的保安劝止并拉进院内进行调查。在西充政府承诺对话和解决问题之后，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>人开始耐心等待西充政府的再次对话，看看政府方面是否有诚意与大家达成一致的解决方案。否则，他们将再次去北京依法表达诉求。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-LpB034kWrjU/UJstHyXEJiI/AAAAAAAATFw/uwc9o0zme-8/s1600/%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259B%25BE00.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"206\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-LpB034kWrjU/UJstHyXEJiI/AAAAAAAATFw/uwc9o0zme-8/s320/%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259B%25BE00.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-7XBVN8Atq0s/UJstJH7x5PI/AAAAAAAATF4/I2zbuNrqoCc/s1600/%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259B%25BE01.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"209\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-7XBVN8Atq0s/UJstJH7x5PI/AAAAAAAATF4/I2zbuNrqoCc/s320/%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259B%25BE01.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-V54yugKNZyI/UJstKJAekvI/AAAAAAAATF8/Srbzk0TnlB4/s1600/%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259B%25BE02.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"212\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-V54yugKNZyI/UJstKJAekvI/AAAAAAAATF8/Srbzk0TnlB4/s320/%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259B%25BE02.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>西充县医院是香港雅博基金会援建的项目。何琼、冯乃如等人为修建该项目提供建筑材料。但在实际修建中，甲方人员贾青﹙县人民医院副院长﹚，在乙方负责人不在的情况下私自动用工程款购买材料，并虚报价格和购买数量，有一笔</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">700</span><span>万元的资金转在私人的帐上。今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月份，公安局经侦小组介入此案，但一直不对资金账目进行清理，也不准乙方负责人核对账目。现在，修建资金缺口很大，根本无法支付材料商冯乃如、何琼等人的材料款。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>，为了讨要血汗钱，何琼等人绝望之余到县公安局，准备用喝农药之举进行抗争，从而希望问题得到解决。结果，换来的是政府更加残酷的打压。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>，何琼等人再次来到县政府办公大楼门前，展示横幅静坐抗议，被十几个警察及政府工作人员抢走横幅，对大家推搡挟持，把他们限制在一个秘密地点进行威逼利诱。坚持维权的何琼等人再次在省委、省政府门口打出横幅。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-7XBVN8Atq0s/UJstJH7x5PI/AAAAAAAATF4/I2zbuNrqoCc/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE01.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-7XBVN8Atq0s/UJstJH7x5PI/AAAAAAAATF4/I2zbuNrqoCc/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE01.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-4057137351006980250?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}